headline: Pinnacle West Sets Date for 2024 Fourth-Quarter and Full-Year Financial Results, Webcast/Conference Call
summary: PHOENIX, January 27, 2025--Pinnacle West plans to release its 2024 fourth-quarter and full-year financial results before U.S. financial markets open on Tuesday, Feb. 25, 2025.
